snippet.title: Amber Heard Wanted 50K/Month in Divorce From Johnny Depp | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Wanted 50K/Month in Divorce From Johnny Depp | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

The case of Johnny Depp and his ex-wife in Amber Heard is one that has divided people in terms of who is right or wrong, who is being protected, and what this says about  cases as a whole. 

Mainly because at first it was made clear that Johnny Depp was an in the relationship, but then evidence started to pop up that it was Amber Heard who was the offender. Amber Heard has been lying and manipulating us this whole time.

All just to gain our sympathy and loyalty. She used this for her own financial gain. Like when tried to get Johnny Depp to pay her $50,000 per month in alimony. Let's tell that story quickly. Allow us to break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
